    Z "Llama a [W] cuando termines para llevar a Fairy a su celda."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2846
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_b8cf3f56:

    # E "Yes, Master. As you wish."
    E "Sí, Amo. Como desees."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2848
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_003949f8:

    # Z "You always give your best, Emilia."
    Z "Siempre das lo mejor de ti, Emilia."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2849
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_f1917430:

    # Z "Continue washing Fairy. Once you're finished notify [W] to take her back to the basement."
    Z "Continúa lavando a Fairy. Cuando hayas terminado, avísale a [W] para llevarla de vuelta al sótano."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2850
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_b8cf3f56_1:

    # E "Yes, Master. As you wish."
    E "Sí, Amo. Como desees."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2854
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_faf3d195:

    # "You head out of the bathroom."
    "Sales del cuarto de baño."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2860
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_045cf30b:

    # "As [E] ends the kiss, Fairy looks at her with a mixture of excitement and confusion."
    "Cuando [E] rompe el beso, Fairy la mira con una mezcla de excitación y confusión."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2863
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_89047b2e:

    # "With [E] resuming her task of bathing Fairy, you figure it's time to leave her to it."
    "Con [E] reanudando su tarea de bañar a Fairy, decides que es hora de dejarlas a lo suyo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2866
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_d89aee35:

    # Z "Well done, Emilia. I'm heading out. Once you're finished, let [W] know so she can take her back to the basement."
    Z "Bien hecho, Emilia. Me voy. Cuando termines, avísale a [W] para que la lleve al sótano."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2869
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_b8cf3f56_2:

    # E "Yes, Master. As you wish."
    E "Sí, Amo. Como desees."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2876
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_0f34faf7:

    # "You watch them for a little while longer, until you've seen enough and decide to leave."
    "Las observas un rato más, hasta que has visto suficiente y decides marcharte."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2877
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_73dc1363:

    # "Fairy seemingly enjoying this, you're sure that she will be a little more relaxed tonight."
    "Como Fairy parece estar disfrutando con esto, estás seguro de que esta noche estará un poco más relajada."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2880
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_73138742:

    # Z "Well done, Emilia. I'm going out. Once you're finished, let [W] know so she can take her back to the basement."
    Z "Bien hecho, Emilia. Voy a salir. Cuando hayas terminado, avisa a [W] para que la lleve al sótano."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2883
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_b8cf3f56_3:

    # E "Yes, Master. As you wish."
    E "Sí, Amo. Como desees."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2890
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_e7f10ba0:

    # "The sun is piercing through the curtained windows as you get into the bathroom, and you see Fairy already lying in the bathtub."
    "El sol atraviesa las ventanas con cortinas cuando entras en el cuarto de baño, y ves a Fairy ya tumbada en la bañera."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2891
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_4b162838:

    # "It looks like your wife already prepared her to get in there."
    "Parece que tu mujer ya la ha preparado para entrar ahí."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2894
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_252748dc:

    # Z "Are you ready?"
    Z "¿Estás preparada?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2895
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_e7913b4a_11:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2896
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_10ddbe94:

    # Z "You definitely need a bath. It must've been a long time since your last opportunity."
    Z "Definitivamente necesitas un baño. Debe haber pasado mucho tiempo desde tu última oportunidad."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2899
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_2328c146:

    # "You take a chair and sit down at the end of the bathtub..."
    "Coges una silla y te sientas al final de la bañera..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2902
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_fc817da6:

    # "Looking at her still hands, it's clear that she doesn't know what to do."
    "Mirando sus manos inmóviles, está claro que no sabe qué hacer."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2903
translate spanish fairy_bath_solo_0617fd41:

    # "Maybe she has forgotten how this feels, or maybe she has never had this much water at her disposal for such a task?"
    "Quizá haya olvidado lo que se siente, o quizá nunca haya tenido tanta agua a su disposición para semejante tarea..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2916
translate spanish basement_fairy_3ca590f1:

    # Zt "Why is she lying under the bed?"
    Zt "¿Por qué está tumbada debajo de la cama?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2921
translate spanish basement_fairy_658a653b:

    # Z "Fairy?"
    Z "¿Fairy?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2924
translate spanish basement_fairy_bcf5f6c2:

    # F "...?!"
    F "¡¿...?!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2927
translate spanish basement_fairy_c36af848:

    # "{i}She hastily gets up...{/i}"
    "{i}Se levanta apresuradamente...{/i}"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2930
translate spanish basement_fairy_334fb1c2:

    # F "Hello Master..."
    F "Hola Amo..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2933
translate spanish basement_fairy_dcbabd9c:

    # F "More, please?"
    F "¿Más, por favor?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2938
translate spanish basement_fairy_ae83f546:

    # Zt "Hasn't changed a bit since the first time I saw her..."
    Zt "No ha cambiado ni un poco desde la primera vez que la vi..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2940
translate spanish basement_fairy_3c533948:

    # Zt "What? Is she always like this?"
    Zt "¿Qué? ¿Siempre es así?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2941
translate spanish basement_fairy_bde5ad34:

    # Z "Drop the act..."
    Z "Deja de actuar..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2942
translate spanish basement_fairy_ec71be58:

    # Z "Tell me, why do you act like this?"
    Z "Dime, ¿por qué actúas así?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2945
translate spanish basement_fairy_e5e3bf68:

    # F "No! No act!"
    F "¡No! ¡No actúo!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2946
translate spanish basement_fairy_0056d1af:

    # F "Master please!"
    F "¡Amo, por favor!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2949
translate spanish basement_fairy_0cd7bbdc:

    # F "Please... I need more..."
    F "Por favor... Necesito más..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2952
translate spanish basement_fairy_30dd516d:

    # F "Will serve.."
    F "Serviré..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2955
translate spanish basement_fairy_ea412c56:

    # Zt "I won't get a word out of her, like this."
    Zt "No conseguiré sacarle ni una palabra de esta manera."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2956
translate spanish basement_fairy_7d17017e:

    # Zt "Maybe there is another way to find out why she acts this way."
    Zt "Tal vez haya otra manera de averiguar por qué actúa de esta manera."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2969
translate spanish basement_fairy_ea33aeeb:

    # Z "You may get what you need."
    Z "Puede que consigas lo que necesitas."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2970
translate spanish basement_fairy_1e165efb:

    # F "...!"
    F "¡...!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2971
translate spanish basement_fairy_67dc02db:

    # Z "But you must be more calm, less frantic."
    Z "But debes estar más tranquila, menos frenética."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2974
translate spanish basement_fairy_ffc34183:

    # F "Yes... calm, caring..."
    F "Sí... tranquila, atenta..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2990
translate spanish basement_fairy_3a84dc2b:

    # Z "I just came to check on you."
    Z "Sólo he venido a ver cómo estabas."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:2993
translate spanish basement_fairy_5eeb2345:

    # "You leave..."
    "Te vas..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3001
translate spanish fairy_talk_1a91e548:

    # Z "Fairy, let go and sit down."
    Z "Fairy, suéltate y siéntate."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3004
translate spanish fairy_talk_62120181:

    # F "Master...?"
    F "¿Amo...?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3007
translate spanish fairy_talk_dbb597df:

    # Z "Just do it."
    Z "Sólo hazlo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3010
translate spanish fairy_talk_ab0434f3:

    # "She does as you say..."
    "Ella hace lo que le dices..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3014
translate spanish fairy_talk_786ebbdd:

    # Z "Stand up."
    Z "Levántate."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3017
translate spanish fairy_talk_6dee973e:

    # F "Mast..-"
    F "Amo..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3020
translate spanish fairy_talk_0b9843a3:

    # Z "I said stand up. And take your clothes off."
    Z "He dicho que te levantes. Y quítate la ropa."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3023
translate spanish fairy_talk_ab0434f3_1:

    # "She does as you say..."
    "Ella hace lo que le dices..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3029
translate spanish fairy_sex_bf40e0dc:

    # Z "Alright, if you want it so badly..."
    Z "De acuerdo, si lo quieres tanto..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3030
translate spanish fairy_sex_427b5485:

    # Z "But you better be gentle; and not too hasty."
    Z "Pero será mejor que seas delicada y que no te precipites."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3033
translate spanish fairy_sex_14612f06:

    # F "Yes... thank you."
    F "Sí... gracias."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3045
translate spanish fairy_sex_7919e0a8:

    # Z "No, you won't."
    Z "No, no lo harás."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3046
translate spanish fairy_sex_99451af5:

    # Z "It's not necessary. You're not required to do this."
    Z "No es necesario. No estás obligada a hacerlo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3049
translate spanish fairy_sex_95b62986:

    # F "But... Master... I need..."
    F "Pero... Amo... necesito..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3052
translate spanish fairy_sex_67c98784:

    # Z "You don't... {i}*sigh*"
    Z "No tienes por qué... {i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3053
translate spanish fairy_sex_f05cb123:

    # "She is so obsessed with serving you, that getting through her is no option for now."
    "Está tan obsesionada con servirte que hacerla entrar en razón es imposible por ahora."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3056
translate spanish fairy_sex_a29b224c:

    # "You step back..."
    "Te alejas..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3057
translate spanish fairy_sex_c33fb3cf:

    # Z "You're not thinking straight."
    Z "No estás pensando con claridad."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3058
translate spanish fairy_sex_6cac33d0:

    # Z "I will see return tomorrow. Come back to your senses, girl."
    Z "Volveré mañana. Vuelve en ti, muchacha."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3061
translate spanish fairy_sex_78e7ccfb:

    # "Ignoring her obsessions, you head out, leaving her to herself..."
    "Pasando de sus obsesiones, sales de allí dejándola sola con sus movidas..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3068
translate spanish fairy_communicate_c57798cd:

    # F "Master, I want-"
    F "Amo, quiero..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3069
translate spanish fairy_communicate_6b3b916b:

    # Z "Fairy... no."
    Z "Hada... no."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3070
translate spanish fairy_communicate_efa2fecb:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3076
translate spanish fairy_communicate_716cd600:

    # Z "Are you feeling okay?"
    Z "¿Te sientes bien?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3077
translate spanish fairy_communicate_3694b4f7:

    # Z "I know this isn't exactly a comfortable place to sleep..."
    Z "Sé que este no es precisamente un lugar cómodo para dormir..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3078
translate spanish fairy_communicate_992291d0:

    # Z "...maybe we can do something about it soon."
    Z "... tal vez pronto podamos hacer algo al respecto."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3079
translate spanish fairy_communicate_0a321fce:

    # Z "But I have to make sure my household is safe, you know."
    Z "Pero tengo que asegurarme de que mi casa está a salvo, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3080
translate spanish fairy_communicate_e7913b4a:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3083
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3085
translate spanish fairy_communicate_ba5c7eff:

    # Z "How long were you in that cage?"
    Z "¿Cuánto tiempo estuviste en esa jaula?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3087
translate spanish fairy_communicate_27b03fc7:

    # Z "How long were you with these two back there?"
    Z "¿Cuánto tiempo estuviste con esos dos allí?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3088
translate spanish fairy_communicate_e7913b4a_1:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3091
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5408543d:

    # F "Master, I want more, please?"
    F "Amo, quiero más, por favor..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3094
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3095
translate spanish fairy_communicate_e3fd34b7:

    # Zt "She seems genuinely eager..."
    Zt "Parece auténticamente ansiosa..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3096
translate spanish fairy_communicate_aa71569f:

    # Zt "And yet, the way she looks at me... I can sense tension in her expression."
    Zt "Y, sin embargo, la forma en que me mira... Puedo percibir tensión en su expresión."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3097
translate spanish fairy_communicate_2780acce:

    # Zt "I have to wait and see."
    Zt "Tengo que esperar y ver."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3102
translate spanish fairy_communicate_7b63d9fe:

    # Z "Tell me..."
    Z "Dime..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3103
translate spanish fairy_communicate_60fbd006:

    # Z "What happened to you?"
    Z "¿Qué te ha pasado?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3104
translate spanish fairy_communicate_33fff82f:

    # Z "I can't risk letting you out of here yet, as long as we can't predict what you will do."
    Z "No puedo arriesgarme a dejarte salir de aquí todavía, mientras no podamos predecir lo que harás."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3105
translate spanish fairy_communicate_569eb66d:

    # Z "But you're safe here. You can tell me anything."
    Z "Pero aquí estás a salvo. Puedes contarme cualquier cosa."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3106
translate spanish fairy_communicate_e7913b4a_2:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3109
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5ab3574d_2:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3110
translate spanish fairy_communicate_58e5f370:

    # Z "What did they do to you?"
    Z "¿Qué te han hecho?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3111
translate spanish fairy_communicate_e7913b4a_3:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3114
translate spanish fairy_communicate_0995a878:

    # F "Master, I'm sorry, I need more."
    F "Amo, lo siento, necesito más."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3117
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5ab3574d_3:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3118
translate spanish fairy_communicate_b49b16c6:

    # Zt "I am not even sure she understands what I'm saying."
    Zt "Ni siquiera estoy seguro de que entienda lo que estoy diciendo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3119
translate spanish fairy_communicate_d33a0371:

    # Zt "Either way, it's too early to tell."
    Zt "En cualquier caso, es demasiado pronto para saberlo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3125
translate spanish fairy_communicate_35caf2f6:

    # Z "Why do you want to serve me?"
    Z "¿Por qué quieres servirme?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3126
translate spanish fairy_communicate_bf953f41:

    # Z "Tell me the truth."
    Z "Dime la verdad."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3129
translate spanish fairy_communicate_b62edead:

    # F "You are Master... please, more."
    F "Eres el Amo... por favor, más."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3130
translate spanish fairy_communicate_db644f7b:

    # F "I serve..."
    F "Yo sirvo..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3133
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5ab3574d_4:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3134
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5da3486e:

    # "You can sense that she has a difficult time waiting for your response..."
    "Puedes sentir que le cuesta esperar tu respuesta..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3140
translate spanish fairy_communicate_c9427b40:

    # Z "You don't need more. And you don't need to do everything."
    Z "No necesitas más. Y no necesitas hacerlo todo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3141
translate spanish fairy_communicate_732a28c1:

    # Z "Maybe you don't trust me yet, but I can assure you of that."
    Z "Tal vez no confíes todavía en mí, pero te aseguro que es así."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3142
translate spanish fairy_communicate_e7913b4a_4:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3147
translate spanish fairy_communicate_2fcdb186:

    # Z "Do you enjoy serving me?"
    Z "¿Disfrutas sirviéndome?"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3150
translate spanish fairy_communicate_3c9553d6:

    # F "Yes, Master!"
    F "¡Sí, Amo!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3151
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5e9faf1e:

    # F "I always enjoy! Please, I need more!"
    F "¡Siempre disfruto! Por favor, ¡necesito más!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3154
translate spanish fairy_communicate_5ab3574d_5:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3163
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_76f56286:

    # Z "I understand that you don't trust me."
    Z "Entiendo que no confíes en mí."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3164
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_8ce43e74:

    # Z "But you need to start talking to me eventually."
    Z "Pero tienes que empezar a hablar conmigo en algún momento."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3165
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_347f97c4:

    # Z "Take all the time you need, you are under no pressure here."
    Z "Tómate todo el tiempo que necesites, aquí no tienes ninguna presión."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3166
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_e7913b4a:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3170
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_ff588a7d:

    # Z "Everyone has their role to play in this house, Fairy."
    Z "Todo el mundo tiene su papel en esta casa, Fairy."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3171
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_7d8eb715:

    # Z "And so do you. But I need to know why you act like this."
    Z "Y tú también. Pero necesito saber por qué actúas así."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3172
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_d37c3c01:

    # Z "Else, we can never find out how to move forward."
    Z "Si no, nunca podremos saber cómo avanzar."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3173
translate spanish fairy_communicate_result_e7913b4a_1:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3179
translate spanish fairy_communicate_end_3e4945f3:

    # "Just as you get up, she rushes over to you..."
    "Justo cuando te levantas, ella se precipita hacia ti..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3182
translate spanish fairy_communicate_end_185ac6ac:

    # F "Master! Don't go, please."
    F "¡Amo! No te vayas, por favor."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3183
translate spanish fairy_communicate_end_bcf34706:

    # F "I can serve more!"
    F "¡Puedo servir más!"

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3186
translate spanish fairy_communicate_end_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3187
translate spanish fairy_communicate_end_5f79600a:

    # Z "You should rest."
    Z "Deberías descansar."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3188
translate spanish fairy_communicate_end_a3635b9a:

    # Z "Just think about what I said."
    Z "Piensa en lo que te he dicho."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3194
translate spanish fairy_communicate_end_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3203
translate spanish fairy_inspect_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3204
translate spanish fairy_inspect_9a0ba4eb:

    # F "Master... I want..."
    F "Amo... Yo quiero..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3207
translate spanish fairy_inspect_c6392529:

    # Z "I have not taken a look at you yet."
    Z "Todavía no te he echado un vistazo."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3208
translate spanish fairy_inspect_e7913b4a:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3211
translate spanish fairy_inspect_1d82a04f:

    # Z "Maybe later."
    Z "Quizá más tarde."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3216
translate spanish fairy_inspect_b7030b17:

    # Z "Shut up."
    Z "Cállate."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3217
translate spanish fairy_inspect_e7913b4a_1:

    # F "..."
    F "..."

# game/scripts/basement.rpy:3220
translate spanish fairy_inspect_d39db8f9:

    # Z "I have not inspected you yet, so stay quiet and let me do my thing."
    Z "Todavía no te he inspeccionado, así que quédate tranquila y déjame hacer lo mío."

